                      "name": "indexText",
                      "fill": "#555555",
                      "content": "Purpose: entry point for sign-in, registration, and system explanation.\nKey UI blocks: hero, login form, signup form, module cards, Firestore collections, onboarding note.\nPrimary action: authenticate, then route users by role.",
