                      "content": "Purpose: give tenants visibility into room, bills, payments, visitors, and account recovery.\nKey UI blocks: summary stats, room detail panel, billing table, payment history, visitor registration + log, password reset, profile update.\nPrimary action: self-service status checking and record submission.",
