                  "name": "flowText",
                  "fill": "#F5F3EF",
                  "content": "1. User lands on index.html and signs in or registers.\n2. assets/app.js checks users/{uid}.role in Firestore.\n3. Admin users route to admin.html.\n4. Tenant users route to tenant.html.\n5. Both dashboards read and write shared Firestore collections based on role-specific actions.",
